Description: Shama 10 is new fragrance for a woman who is designed for the glamorous, daring, brave, and very sexy girls who like to party and enjoy themselves. the fragrance is an intense oriental - floral and is based on notes of orange blossom, symbolizing italian femininity, sensuality and extravagance. there are also ambery - oriental nuances of benzoin, pink pepper, tonka and vanilla. the fragrance is available as 100 ml eau de parfum.

Title: Shama Deep Intense Series Alcohol Free, Undiluted Eau de Parfum  -  60 ml(For Women)
Description: The fragrance is very calm with aquatic notes that remind us of ocean breeze and cool sea-water, fruits and woods. top notes are luscious, cool and aquatic with citrus, honeydew melon, quince, pineapple, lotus and lily. heart notes are gentle flowers; may rose, jasmine and muguet. base notes are musk, vanilla, peach, sandalwood, orris and vetiver.

Title: BIRRA BEAMISH Eau de Parfum  -  100 ml(For Men & Women, Men, Women, Boys, Girls, Boys & Girls)
Description: Woody-Oriental Composition that will make you feel fresh and lasts long. An exotic overshadow of the classic woody Sophisticated and Playful Aroma. Blend of Warm and Sensual Fruits & Wood, Low Notes of Vanilla and Musk. Ruby-red glass - Attractive and Modern Design

Title: Shama Black Diamond Series Alcohol Free, Undiluted Eau de Parfum  -  60 ml(For Men)
Description: Black diamond is a modern, masculine fragrance for men. the perfume starts with a fresh wave of rosemary and citruses (bergamot, mandarin orange) combined with airy notes of violet leaves. the heart is made of bay leaf, nutmeg, mint, insence and peppermint. the base introduces intense notes of cypress, guaiac tree, sandalwood, amber and musk.

Title: Shama Diamond Series Alcohol Free, Undiluted Eau de Parfum  -  60 ml(For Women)
Description: Shama diamond is a fragrance which is classified as gourmand-floral. the top notes are litchi and raspberry, the middle notes are freesia and lily of the valley, and the base are vetiver, cedar wood, patchouli and vanilla. we're using the rose but in a very gourmand way, like a flower that can be eaten'. the perfume will come in 60ml bottles.

Title: Shama 36-Degree Series Alcohol Free, Undiluted Eau de Parfum  -  60 ml(For Men)
Description: 36 degree is dark and powerful, as if it were announcing powerful ingredients it carries in itself. a veil of mystery and an explosive spicy accord reveal cardamom with sparkling freshness of bergamot, lavender and cedar, which stand for strength of men. cumin and vetiver in a base ensure a sensual finish and an opulent, elegant closure.

Title: Shama Black Shams Series Alcohol Free, Undiluted Eau de Parfum  -  60 ml(For Men)
Description: Black shams wafts like a breeze through the dunes of a desert. the fragrance seduces with classic middle eastern incense notes topping a heart of mysterious oud and the sweetness and depth of amber. the lingering soft musky base notes leave a final memory of the sweet seduction.

Title: Shama Volcano Series Alcohol Free, Undiluted Eau de Parfum  -  60 ml(For Men)
Description: Volcano is a sophisticated and contemporary fragrance from shama. the fragrance is dedicated to freedom-endless, deep and boundless. the woody-aromatic composition followed the original path but goes down into a sensual and oriental amber territory. wood maintains the freshness of the original in this variant, enriched with depth and velvet amber woods including grapefruit.

Title: Shama Berry Berry Series Alcohol Free, Undiluted Eau de Parfum  -  60 ml(For Women)
Description: Berry berry is a fragrance that keeps the tradition but with a modern sound, it brings the english irony and english dignity this unisex perfume celebrates the tropical splendor and exotic scent. it opens with a citrusy cocktail of white bergamot, blue berry, jamaican lime, sicilian mandarin. the citruses are accompanied by a note of copra, the white inner flesh of the coconut. the heart includes intensive indian jasmine and sweet hibiscus, exotic ylang-ylang and cold, spicy ginger. the base of the composition includes sugar cane & musk.

Title: Shama Dollsy Series Alcohol Free, Undiluted Eau de Parfum  -  100 ml(For Women)
Description: Shama dollsy is described as a soft and feminine scent of white flowers. freshness of neroli leaf together with papaya flower open the composition making an introduction to the heart that dominates with white amaryllis, narcissus and white water lily. the base is soft with cashmere and musk.

Title: Shama 70-Series Alcohol Free, Undiluted Eau de Parfum  -  100 ml(For Men)
Description: Shama 70 is a woody aromatic fragrance for men. in addition to a common sporting note, each possesses a different olfactory character. shama70 represents simplicity, elegance, freshness, symbolizes intensity, aquatic life, manhood, nature and good vibrations. top notes are lime, lavender, clary sage, bergamot and lemon; middle notes are carnation, green notes, galbanum, basil, jasmine and geranium; base notes are tonka bean, amber, musk, oakmoss, vetiver and cedar. the fragrance is available as 100 ml eau de parfum.

Title: Shama Rush Series Alcohol Free, Undiluted Eau de Parfum  -  60 ml(For Men)
Description: Shama rush is an aromatic woody fragrance that exudes elegance representing a contrast between clean, fresh and rich, warm aromas. announced as the scent of pure instinct and emotion that is express freely; the fragrance is the force of a determined man, with a heart that is rooted in tradition, yet revels in the modern world. the composition opens with fresh aquatic notes and green nuances of basil and lavender. the new chord in the world of fragrance moepel wood from south africa makes the heart with its luxurious floral, balsamic and honey accents. tobacco is deepened by dry notes of hay absolute and bran. the intensity and strength of the composition come from the base of labdanum, sandalwood and cypress.

Title: ARMAF Just For You Eau de Toilette  -  100 ml(For Men)
Description: An intense woody scent mixed with fresh and spicy notes of green mandarin, pink pepper nutmeg and birch leaves. The heart composes of cedarwood, patchouli and vetiver leading to a base of incense and leathery notes.

Description: The French perfume house Robert Piguet introduced the new collection intended for the Asian market, The Pacific Collection de Robert Piguet. It consists of three fragrances inspired by symbolic plants of China Blossom, Chai and Jeunesse.With Jeunesse, Robert Piguet offers a lighthearted and vivacious fragrance that is as elegant as it is tempting. Mouthwatering like a raspberry macaron and flirty like a silk summer dress, Jeneusse charms with its alluring sweetness. Jenuesse which means youth is a fresh fruity floral fragrance built on the contrast of sweet raspberry and sour pomegranate notes. It is joyful and the most intense of all three in the collection. Jeunesse was launched in 2012.
